1.	安裝XAMPP
https://www.apachefriends.org/zh_tw/download.html 
 
2.	安裝Composer
https://getcomposer.org/download/ 
 
3.	安裝Laravel
進入Terminal輸入：
composer global require laravel/installer

4.	建立專案
cd c:\xampp\htdocs
composer create-project --prefer-dist laravel/laravel blog

5.	設定hosts (設定站台的網址)
Windows 版本請至 C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc\hosts
設定範例  127.0.0.1   blog.test

6.	設定 vhosts (設定vhosts可以達到同一個伺服器架設多個網站的功能)
Windows 版本請至C:\xampp\apache\conf\extra\httpd-vhosts.conf
<VirtualHost  *:80>
    DocumentRoot "C:\xampp\htdocs\blog\public"
    ServerAdmin blog.test
	  ServerName blog.test
	  ErrorLog "logs/ blog.test -error.log"
    CustomLog "logs/ blog.test -access.log" combined
    <Directory "C:\xampp\htdocs\blog\public">
        Options All
        AllowOverride All
        Require all granted
    </Directory>
</VirtualHost>
